{"tid":2164223,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[純文字討論]試過有咩吱暗瘡嘅核突經歷？","createTime":"2020-08-19T05:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T06:10:27.000Z","uid":57308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b6c560c139b460cbe22634b5d5e0f30c4b668f","tid":2164223,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:51:42.000Z","msg":"有次個鼻生咗粒 硬係覺得吱唔乾淨<br />\n死吱爛吱，用埋指甲去夾<br />\n最後好似吱咗塊粉紅色嘅肉出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有次ex背脊生咗粒唔知乜瘡<br />\n佢搽過好多消炎嘢都冇用，又唔想去睇醫生<br />\n跟住搵我幫手吱<br />\n我一嘢就吱爆咗，仲噴到我個鼻同嘴唇都有<br />\n佢本來都忍到痛，見到我俾佢顏射完，即刻爆喊<br />\n望住佢喊到咁撚委屈個樣<br />\n我一邊扮安慰佢一邊心諗要喊都係我喊啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a847991527d104b6cab7b8900a05aba183b3a7","tid":2164223,"uid":11862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"你下次都射落佢塊面跟住喊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5084f4a12f9e0edb919504219d6ee70545b863","tid":2164223,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60a847991527d104b6cab7b8900a05aba183b3a7","tid":2164223,"uid":11862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"你下次都射落佢塊面跟住喊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496e8f895ce09a51e82a4415371b164eb115c422","tid":2164223,"uid":205742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}